These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, lilac, light-blue, aquamarine
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, bolivar, chaman, ritmeester
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, aconite, marigold, daffodil
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, trike, ship, train
1. the bolivar-smoker is the person who likes coral##1
2. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
3. the person who growsmarigold is the game-smoker##1
4. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
5. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
6. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
7. the bolivar-smoker is the person driving the helicopter##1
8. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
9. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Color         | coral  | aquamarine  | lilac | light-blue |
| Cigar           | bolivar | game | ritmeester  | chaman  |
| Flower   | daffodil       | marigold      | dahlia | aconite      |
| Transport           | helicopter          | trike     | ship    | train     |

