.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, baking, cooking, drawing
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, lizard, ferret, mouse
4 different games are played: backgammon, go, billiard, snooker
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, action, disaster, musical
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far right##1
2. the person playing snooker is the person watching family movies##1
3. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
5. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person playing billiard##1
7. the person playing go is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
8. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
9. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby      | cooking     | gardening       | baking | drawing        |
| Pet          | mouse     | lizard       | ferret   | guinea-pig   |
| Game   | billiard      | go       | snooker     | backgammon    |
| Movie-Genre         | disaster | musical | family | action |

