.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
House: futuristic, cottage, ranch-style, farmhouse
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, broccoli, apple, peach
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, marigold, balloon-flower, amaryllis
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, jazz, trance, dubstep
 1. the farmhouse house is the fan of dubstep##1
 2. the ranch-style house is on the far right##1
 3. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the far right##1
 4. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
 5. the futuristic house is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
 6. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
 7. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
 8. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
 9. the futuristic house is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
10. the ranch-style house is the person eating peach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| House      | cottage | futuristic       | farmhouse        | ranch-style        |
| Food           | broccoli   | apple | cauliflower   | peach |
| Flower   | orchid     | marigold    | amaryllis | balloon-flower        |
| Music-Genre           | trance         | salsa  | dubstep       | jazz         |

