3. the gothic-revival house is on the far right##1
4. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
5. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the modern house##1
6. the tower house is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
7. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
8. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1
9. the havana-smoker is the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| Flower           | poppy   | iris  | marigold | dahlia |
| House   | cape-cod | tower       | modern       | gothic-revival     |
| Beverage   | milk       | mirinda    | juice     | cola  |
