4 different games are played: poker, chess, domino, monopoly
City: boston, berlin, marseilles, london
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, baking, reading
1. the person playing domino is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left##1
4. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
5. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
6. the person who's hobby is reading is the person traveling to marseilles##1
7. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person playing poker##1
8. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the person playing chess##1
9. the person playing poker is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Cigar           | alhambra  | pall-mall    | ritmeester | oliveros |
| Game   | domino      | chess    | poker         | monopoly    |
| City   | berlin   | boston     | marseilles          | london      |
| Hobby         | camping | board-games | reading      | baking      |

