The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, volleyball, basketball, tennis
House: futuristic, tower, victorian, gothic-revival
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, white, light-blue, azure
 1. the fan of rock is the futuristic house##1
 2. the fan of punk is the tower house##1
 3. the person who's sport is badminton is the futuristic house##1
 4. the person who likes light-blue is the fan of punk##1
 5. the victorian house is the person who's sport is tennis##1
 6. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
 7. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
 8. the futuristic house is on the right of the victorian house##1
 9. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
10. the person who likes red is on the left of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Music-Genre          | punk  | salsa | rock     | r&b |
| Sport           | basketball  | tennis      | badminton | volleyball    |
| House   | tower | victorian  | futuristic    | gothic-revival  |
| Color           | light-blue   | azure       | red       | white      |

