 8. the person driving the subway is the person eating strawberry##1
 9. the person eating cauliflower is on the far right##1
10. the person playing go is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4     |
| Hobby      | chess | cooking     | rock-climbing          | traveling |
| Game   | go   | monopoly       | whist     | billiard   |
| Transport   | subway    | jet-ski  | trike         | scooter     |
| Food         | strawberry | peas | kale | cauliflower  |

 